Package: testpackage
Type: Package
Title: Resisuals and Outlier Influence in Linear Regression 
Version: 0.1.0
Author: JiaxinQian
Maintainer: <jiaxinq@umich.edu>
Description: Compute leverage values in X space of a linear regression model, three commonly used resisuals (standardized, internally studentized, and externally studentized residuals), and diagnostic statistics for identifying outliers (DFFITS, Cook's Distance, and COVRATIO) with their individual plotting functions.  
